title: Shehzaade
subTitle: Suraj, a justice-loving man, must face a series of obstacles when he discovers his widowed mother's affair with a former prisoner.

title: Chalte Chalte
subTitle: Geeta is admitted to a psychiatric hospital after her lover passes away tragically. Later, she gains her senses, only to find him alive and in love with another woman.

title: Main Intequam Loonga
subTitle: Kumar learns that his father, a national level boxing champion, was killed when he refused to lose a fight. He vows to annihilate his father's killers, unaware that he may face tragic consequences.

title: Khel Khilari Ka
subTitle: Ajit swears revenge after witnessing his family's murder by three thugs. Years later, he becomes a wealthy crime lord, but he still thirsts for revenge.

title: Katilon Ke Kaatil
subTitle: Traumatised by her murder of her husband and the abduction of her two sons, a woman spends her life looking for her family. Things take a turn when two men arrive at her house with a family heirloom.

title: Prithvi
subTitle: When Prithvi and Neha, a newly-wed couple, travel abroad for their honeymoon, Neha goes missing. Later, he fights against all odds to rescue her.

title: Prem Deewane
subTitle: A young couple in love run away together after their parents oppose their relationship. They are misguided into kidnapping a wealthy person for a big ransom by a shrewd uncle who has his own agenda.

title: Ganga Tere Desh Mein
subTitle: After arresting and institutionalising a notorious criminal who has lost his mental faculties, inspector Ajay finds his mother feeding the criminal. But when he digs deeper he uncovers a tragic truth.

title: Mr. Natwarlal
subTitle: When Natwar's elder brother is framed for bribery, he decides to avenge his brother's humiliation and thus poses as a crime lord.

title: Mr. Natwarlal
subTitle: When Natwar's elder brother is framed for bribery, he decides to avenge his brother's humiliation and thus poses as a crime lord.

title: Gurudev
subTitle: Dev Kumar, a police inspector, finds himself in a dilemma when has to arrest a notorious criminal who also happens to the father of his childhood friend, Guru.

title: Aakhri Ghulam
subTitle: Bheema and his family live under the tyranny of their master, Daulat Singh. But, when Bheema revolts, his love for his master's daughter is threatened.

title: Maati Maangey Khoon
subTitle: Hariya is clueless about his parents and discovers that his family was destroyed by Thakur Balram Singh. He vows to take revenge, especially after his friend, who is Balram's nephew, also opposes him.

title: China Gate
subTitle: Colonel Puri requests his former fellow army officers court-martialed in disgrace to redeem themselves by rescuing a village from Jageera, an evil bandit.

title: Khuda Kasam
subTitle: CBI Officer Neetu Singh is framed for the assassination of a chief minister. She then attempts to solve this murder mystery with the help of a man, who is imprisoned for a crime he never committed.

title: Parivaar
subTitle: When a young girl is thrown out of her home by her evil relatives, she finds shelter with a poor street performer and his two children, a dog and a monkey.

title: Teri Meherbaniyan
subTitle: Ram, an honest man, falls in love with a woman named Bijli and goes on to help the people of her village. However, the region's corrupt leader, Thakur Vijay Singh, soon begins to plot against him.

title: Juaari
subTitle: The struggle against a dangerous gambling lord tests Dharam Singh and Vijay as they navigate crime, deception and violence to protect the innocent and reclaim what was lost.

title: Juaari
subTitle: The struggle against a dangerous gambling lord tests Dharam Singh and Vijay as they navigate crime, deception and violence to protect the innocent and reclaim what was lost.

title: Aulad
subTitle: Believing his wife to be dead, Anand gives up his own child to Yashoda, who has lost her husband and her baby. However, he faces a dilemma when his wife returns.

title: Haisiyat
subTitle: Ram, a union leader, falls in love with the factory's new owner, Sita. However, management disputes create complications in their relationship.

title: Wafadaar
subTitle: Chanda's parents disapprove of her boyfriend Ranga and want her to marry Prasad. Ranga is accused of having an affair with Sita.

title: 15th August
subTitle: Nagpal kills Chaudhry and his son, Ram, a military officer. Chaudhry's second son, Vikram, vows to destroy Nagpal who is all set to become the Chief Minister on the upcoming Indian Independence Day.

title: Shiva Shakti
subTitle: Shiva forms a close friendship with Shakti when he comes to the city to earn money for his sister Kusum's wedding. However, he later vows to kill Shakti when Kusum becomes pregnant with his child.

title: Dil Hi to Hai
subTitle: Twin brothers swap identities in childhood, unknowingly setting the stage for emotional turmoil, romantic confusion, and conflicts tied to their royal lineage.

title: Taqdeer Ka Tamasha
subTitle: An officer has a strained relationship with his brother Satya, a criminal. While attempting to gather evidence against a goon, he meets his sibling. But, they are not aware of the gangster's secrets.

title: Ghatak / Lethal
subTitle: For his father's treatment, Kashi and his father move into a colony on the outskirts of Mumbai. But when Kashi sees a local gangster terrorise the colony, he decides to strike back.
